Features
GraphQL API for managing employee data.
Authentication & Authorization: Role-based access control for Admin and Employee roles.
CRUD Operations: Admin can add, update, and view employee data; Employees can view data.
Pagination & Sorting: List employees with pagination and sorting options.
Performance Optimizations for efficient data retrieval.

git clone <repository-url>
cd employee-management-app

npm install

node src/server.js
